logic.bankSelection

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.bankSelection.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that implements an Entry of a bank. An entry consists out of a reference to a domino and a reference to the player which selected this specific domino. Both fields may be null.
